%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20sucks%20to%20live%20next%20to%20a%20data%20center%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223405%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20neighborhood%20with%20a%20data%20center%20in%20the%20background%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f1ac6ad288d1480d034%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Amazon%20data%20center%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20Loudoun%20Meadows%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20many%20neighborhoods%20in%20northern%20Virginia%20witnessing%20data%20center%20development.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMustafa%20Kaya%20thought%20he%20had%20found%20his%20perfect%20home%20in%20a%20Northern%20Virginia%20neighborhood%20called%20Amberleigh%20Station%2C%20drawn%20to%20the%20serenity%20of%20the%20evergreen%20woods%20that%20border%20his%20backyard.%20As%20a%20data%20scientist%20and%20first-time%20homeowner%2C%20Kaya%20wanted%20a%20quiet%20place%20where%20he%20could%20raise%20his%20family.%20Then%20came%20the%20noise%3A%20Google%20was%20building%20a%20data%20center%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20those%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEquipment%20testing%20can%20be%20so%20loud%20that%20Kaya%20once%20resorted%20to%20sleeping%20in%20the%20basement%20for%20two%20nights.%20The%20neighborhood%20air%20carries%20wafts%20of%20diesel%20fumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaya's%20neighbor%20Donna%20Gallant%20said%20she%20had%20awakened%20to%20jackhammering%20before%206%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20considering%20restarting%20the%20antianxiety%20medications%20she's%20been%20free%20of%20for%20years.%20A%20homeowner%20in%20another%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20county%20said%20blasting%20for%20a%20data%20center%20project%20there%20cracked%20their%20drywall.%20The%20droning%20of%20the%20cooling%20fans%20from%20the%20now-operating%20facility%20has%20disturbed%20one%20family's%20young%20son%2C%20who%20they%20say%20has%20had%20nightmares%20about%20aliens%20landing%20a%20spaceship%20outside%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20impacts%20on%20Virginia%20residents%20grappling%20with%20an%20unprecedented%20construction%20boom%20for%20data%20centers%2C%20the%20large%20warehouses%20filled%20with%20computer%20servers%20powering%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20cloud%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20influx%20has%20brought%20new%20jobs%20and%20more%20tax%20revenue%20to%20pay%20for%20community%20improvements.%20It%20also%20has%20fueled%20discord%20in%20Prince%20William%20County%2C%20where%20Kaya%20and%20his%20neighbors%20live%2C%20roiling%20local%20politics%20over%20the%20impact%20on%20housing%2C%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20a%20national%20park%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20first%20major%20Civil%20War%20battle.%20The%20changes%20are%20pitting%20homeowners%20devoted%20to%20their%20quality%20of%20life%20against%20other%20residents%20looking%20to%20sell%20to%20the%20next%20data%20center%20project%2C%20and%20have%20swept%20up%20elected%20officials%20trying%20to%20find%20some%20middle%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20is%20the%20epicenter%20of%20an%20AI-driven%20construction%20wave%20rippling%20across%20America.%20A%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%20of%20US%20data%20centers%20found%20that%20many%20are%20located%20in%20population%20centers%2C%20where%20they%20bring%20disruption%20as%20well%20as%20opportunity.%20Indeed%2C%20of%20the%201%2C240%20data%20centers%20that%20have%20been%20built%20or%20approved%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Business%20Insider%20found%20that%20roughly%20half%20are%20within%20a%20mile%20of%20at%20least%205%2C000%20people.%20(See%20here%20for%20more%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calculate-data-center-cost-environmental-impact-methodology-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20methodology%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2025%2F06%2F2025-06-data-centers-itsucks-map%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22map%5C%22%20data-sequence%3D%5C%22va-datacenters%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20center%20industry%20first%20took%20root%20next%20door%20in%20Virginia's%20Loudoun%20County%2C%20which%20has%20approved%20permits%20for%20176%20facilities%20or%20clusters%20of%20data%20centers%20called%20%26quot%3Bcampuses.%26quot%3B%20Loudoun%2C%20nicknamed%20Data%20Center%20Alley%2C%20became%20a%20tech%20magnet%20almost%20by%20accident.%20The%20early%20internet%20service%20provider%20UUNet%20Communications%20helped%20establish%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20exchange%20points%20beneath%20Loudoun%2C%20strategically%20near%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20roughly%20halfway%20down%20the%20Atlantic%20seaboard.%20State%20officials%20seeking%20new%20investment%20and%20jobs%20offered%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20industry%20tax%20breaks%2C%20and%20county%20authorities%20rolled%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%2C%20offering%20an%20advantageous%20regulatory%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20data%20center%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f193fe8d3928365ba2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20massive%20data%20center%20campus%20under%20construction%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%26quot%3BData%20Center%20Alley%26quot%3B%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%2C%20the%20nation's%20largest%20cluster%20of%20data%20centers.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facilities%20were%20smaller%20then%2C%20often%20clustered%20in%20corporate%20office%20parks.%20As%20the%20buildings%20got%20bigger%20and%20more%20numerous%2C%20companies%20started%20scanning%20for%20sites%20slightly%20farther%20afield.%20Prince%20William%20now%20has%2077%20campuses%20built%20or%20underway%2C%20including%2040%20owned%20by%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Virginia's%20legislature%20took%20a%20step%20back%20to%20assess.%20%26quot%3BThe%20industrial%20scale%20of%20data%20centers%20makes%20them%20largely%20incompatible%20with%20residential%20uses%2C%26quot%3B%20auditors%20with%20the%20Joint%20Legislative%20Audit%20and%20Review%20Commission%20found%20in%20their%20156-page%20report.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20local%20ordinances%20allowed%20data%20centers%20to%20be%20built%20cheek%20by%20jowl%20with%20residential%20neighborhoods%2C%20or%20local%20officials%20signed%20off%20on%20zoning%20exceptions%20or%20rezonings%20that%20accomplished%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20almost%20a%20third%20of%20the%20operating%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20state%20are%20sited%20within%20200%20feet%20of%20residential%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20complaints%20of%20Kaya%20and%20his%20neighbors%2C%20but%20it%20and%20other%20data%20center%20companies%20say%20their%20investments%20benefit%20the%20local%20economy%20and%20community.%20Some%20residents%20also%20welcome%20the%20data%20center%20boom%2C%20which%20they%20see%20as%20providing%20needed%20tax%20revenue%20without%20overburdening%20public%20infrastructure%20like%20roads%20or%20schools.%20Loudon%20counts%20itself%20among%20the%20fastest-growing%20counties%20in%20America%20with%20a%20population%20over%20100%2C000.%20Homeowners%20have%20watched%20the%20median%20sales%20price%20rise%20more%20than%2070%25%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20are%20drawn%20to%20a%20quality%20of%20life%20enabled%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20tax%20revenue%20from%20data%20centers%2C%20Buddy%20Rizer%2C%20the%20county's%20executive%20director%20of%20economic%20development%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20Loudoun%20County%20collected%20%24875%20million%20in%20tax%20revenue%20from%20data%20centers%20in%20its%202024%20fiscal%20year%2C%20which%20Rizer%20said%20had%20helped%20fund%20schools%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20other%20services%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20tax%20cut%20that%20he%20said%20was%20saving%20homeowners%20about%20%243%2C500%20a%20year%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20surging%20population%20is%20heightening%20competition%20for%20open%20space%20and%20making%20it%20more%20likely%20that%20data%20centers%20are%20close%20to%20population%20centers.%20Prince%20William%20County's%20bucolic%20environs%20are%20vanishing.%20Kaya's%20scenic%20backyard%20view%20is%20now%20marred%20by%20a%20line%20of%20orange%20surveyor's%20tape%20snaking%20through%20the%20trees%2C%20marking%20the%20boundaries%20for%20future%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20data%20center%20next%20to%20a%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f1ac6ad288d1480d033%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Amazon%20data%20center%20by%20Loudoun%20Meadows%20looms%20over%20a%20small%20park.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20are%20racing%20to%20get%20out.%20One%20resident%20of%20Amberleigh%20Station%20quickly%20put%20their%20house%20up%20for%20sale%20after%20receiving%20a%20certified%20letter%2C%20with%20an%20enclosed%20map%2C%20alerting%20residents%20to%20a%20forthcoming%20project%20that%20would%20clear%20the%20trees%20surrounding%20the%20community%20on%20three%20sides%20to%20build%2011%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20one%20look%20at%20it%20and%20said%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20resident.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20a%20good%20quality%20of%20life.%26quot%3B%20The%20couple%20ended%20up%20selling%20what%20they%20once%20thought%20was%20their%20%26quot%3Bforever%20home%26quot%3B%20for%20more%20than%20the%20listing%20price%20and%20moving%20to%20another%20county%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20trying%20to%20exit%20strategically%2C%20seeking%20to%20organize%20their%20neighbors%20to%20sell%20their%20homes%20together%20to%20the%20highest%20data%20center%20bidder.%20Gallant%20said%20she%20had%20been%20in%20talks%20to%20do%20that%20within%20Amberleigh%20Station.%20Efforts%20are%20underway%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20county.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20property%20owners%20along%20Pageland%20Lane%2C%20in%20a%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20county%2C%20became%20the%20first%20large%20group%20to%20begin%20selling%20to%20the%20data%20centers%20in%202021.%20For%20nearly%20%241%20million%20an%20acre%20for%20some%2C%20they%20agreed%20to%20sell%20some%202%2C100%20acres%20to%20Compass%20Datacenters%20and%20QTS%2C%20a%20data%20center%20company%20owned%20by%20the%20Wall%20Street%20investing%20giant%20Blackstone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20project%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Prince%20William%20Digital%20Gateway%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20transform%20part%20of%20the%20county's%20protected%20rural%20area%20and%20nestle%20up%20against%20Manassas%20National%20Battlefield%20Park%2C%20which%20commemorates%20the%20first%20and%20second%20battles%20of%20Bull%20Run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20sale%20ignited%20a%20backlash%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20departure%20of%20at%20least%20two%20county%20supervisors.%20One%2C%20Pete%20Candland%2C%20reversed%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20Digital%20Gateway%20project%20around%20the%20time%20his%20property%20was%20included%20in%20its%20final%20footprint.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20Candland%20resigned%20after%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Commonwealth's%20Attorney%20said%20it%20could%20be%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20for%20him%20to%20vote%20on%20future%20data%20center%20projects%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20Another%20supervisor%2C%20Ann%20Wheeler%2C%20lost%20a%20primary%20in%202023%20to%20a%20challenger%20who%20campaigned%20on%20criticism%20of%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWheeler%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20issue%20wasn't%20the%20only%20reason%20she%20lost%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20the%20opponents%20of%20the%20data%20center%20issue%20jumped%20on%20not%20because%20they%20were%20affected%20by%20a%20data%20center%20but%20because%20NIMBYism%20has%20advanced%20to%20BANANAism.%20Build%20Absolutely%20Nothing%20Anywhere%20Near%20Anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20residents%2C%20the%20data%20centers'%20sound%20rankles%20the%20most%2C%20a%20relentless%20whir%20of%20fans%20and%20cooling%20equipment%20that%20drowns%20out%20nature%2C%20invades%20conversation%2C%20and%20impedes%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20and%20other%20companies%20say%20they%20invest%20significantly%20in%20noise%20control%20efforts.%20Even%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20issue%20can%20fuel%20tensions%20with%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Yanes'%20home%20sits%20higher%20than%20many%20of%20his%20neighbors'%20in%20the%20Great%20Oak%20neighborhood%20in%20Prince%20William.%20Where%20that%20once%20provided%20a%20welcoming%20perch%20to%20hear%20the%20surrounding%20wildlife%2C%20it%20now%20puts%20him%20within%20range%20of%20the%20noise%20coming%20from%20Amazon's%20data%20centers.%20He%20has%20felt%20the%20sound%20inside%20his%20house%20for%20most%20of%20the%20three%20years%20the%20facility%20has%20been%20operating%20and%20said%20he%20had%20to%20move%20his%20family's%20sleeping%20quarters%20to%20the%20basement%20to%20get%20any%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYanes%2C%20who%20works%20in%20the%20heating%20and%20cooling%20industry%2C%20spent%20almost%20%2420%2C000%20to%20replace%20his%20windows%20but%20it%20didn't%20fix%20the%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20standing%20in%20his%20backyard%20and%20raising%20his%20voice%20to%20be%20heard%20over%20a%20low%20drone%20from%20the%20Amazon%20facility.%20He%20says%20his%20son%20has%20been%20having%20nightmares%20in%20which%20the%20noise%20is%20actually%20a%20spaceship%20that%20has%20landed%20in%20the%20yard.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20good%20thing%20to%20be%20experiencing%20as%20a%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2025%2F04%2F2025-04-data-centers-summaries%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22summary-audioScrubber%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20for%20public%20officials%20is%20that%20noise%20ordinances%20are%20typically%20crafted%20to%20capture%20intermittent%20noises%2C%20like%20firecrackers%20or%20house%20parties%20or%20jackhammers%2C%20not%20the%20constant%20drone%20given%20off%20by%20a%20data%20center.%20Yanes%20has%20been%20collecting%20sound%20measurements%20from%20his%20deck%20and%20sharing%20them%20with%20Dale%20Browne%2C%20his%20homeowner%20association's%20former%20president.%20Their%20readings%20show%20that%20the%20lower-frequency%20data%20center%20noise%20driving%20Yanes'%20family%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20basement%20doesn't%20often%20violate%20existing%20ordinances%2C%20which%20are%20written%20to%20measure%20standard%20midrange%20sounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20American%20Public%20Health%20Association%2C%20chronic%20noise%20exposure%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20problems%2C%20including%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20sleep%20disruption%2C%20and%20increased%20stress%20that%20can%20cause%20psychological%20disorders%20or%20early%20death.%20Children%20are%20among%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrowne%20has%20shared%20Yanes'%20noise%20findings%20with%20county%20officials%20and%20executives%20at%20Amazon%2C%20which%20beginning%20in%202022%20made%20changes%20such%20as%20adding%20sound-dampening%20material%20to%20the%20fans%20and%20changing%20the%20shutters%20that%20allow%20air%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Miller%2C%20vice%20president%20for%20global%20data%20centers%20at%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20the%20company's%20cloud-computing%20division%2C%20said%20Amazon%20initially%20sought%20to%20verify%20whether%20its%20facilities%20were%20responsible%20for%20reported%20noise%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20lots%20of%20sources%20of%20sound%20potentially%20in%20these%20communities.%26quot%3B%20When%20it%20confirmed%20the%20noises%20coming%20from%20its%20data%20centers%2C%20it%20invested%20substantially%2C%20Miller%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20centers%20now%20operate%20well%20below%20required%20levels%20and%20that%20Amazon%20doesn't%20detect%20sound%20emissions%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bdifferentiable%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ambient%20noise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20data%20centers%20having%20a%20very%20minimal%20effect%20on%20communities%20at%20large%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20reduced%2C%20but%20didn't%20eliminate%2C%20the%20noise%2C%20according%20to%20Browne%20and%20Yanes.%20Browne%20is%20now%20pressing%20the%20county%20to%20get%20its%20noise%20ordinance%20updated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20lawmakers%20passed%20a%20bill%20during%20the%202025%20session%20that%20would%20have%20directed%20local%20governments%20to%20require%20applicants%20to%20perform%20a%20noise%20analysis%20for%20potential%20data%20center%20sites.%20Virginia%20Gov.%20Glenn%20Youngkin%20has%20said%20that%20the%20testing%20should%20be%20optional%2C%20and%20that%20the%20legislature%20must%20reconsider%20the%20bill%20when%20it%20reconvenes%20next%20year%2C%20leaving%20the%20legislation's%20future%20in%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EVirginia's%20329%20data%20centers%20are%20mostly%20low-slung%20buildings%20that%20sprawl%20across%20the%20landscape.%20They%20have%20transformed%20open%20lots%2C%20fields%2C%20forests%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20into%20structures%20and%20paved%20parking%20lots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20center%20sites%20cover%207%2C200%20acres%20in%20Virginia%2C%20with%20the%20facilities%20themselves%20occupying%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20that%20space%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Virginia%20legislative%20commission's%20report.%20Loudoun%20and%20Prince%20William%20counties%20together%20have%20more%20than%2085%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20data%20centers%20built%20or%20in%20development%2C%20an%20area%20equivalent%20to%201%2C485%20football%20fields%2C%20and%20almost%20as%20much%20zoned%20for%20future%20data%20center%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20transform%20landscapes%2C%20in%20hundreds%20of%20acres%20at%20a%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kathy%20Kulick%2C%20the%20vice%20chair%20of%20a%20group%20of%20HOAs%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%20that%20have%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20industry's%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Data%20center%20construction%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f203fe8d3928365ba31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Microsoft%20data%20center%20under%20construction%20in%20Prince%20William%20County%2C%20Virginia.%20The%20county%20has%2025%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20planning%20or%20construction%20phases.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlora%20and%20fauna%20may%20suffer.%20In%20Fairfax%20County%2C%20just%20outside%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20Beltway%2C%20a%20data%20center%20development%20threatens%20a%20nesting%20place%20for%20great%20blue%20herons%2C%20the%20solitary%20aquatic%20birds%20often%20seen%20standing%20in%20the%20shallow%20waters%20of%20local%20rivers%20and%20streams.%20Some%20residents%20fear%20that%20the%20development%20%E2%80%94%20managed%20by%20Penzance%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20developer%20that%20says%20its%20%26quot%3Bgoal%20is%20to%20leave%20everything%20better%20than%20we%20found%20it%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20could%20disrupt%20the%20natural%20environment%20of%20a%20small%20but%20healthy%20aquatic%20ecosystem%20called%20Cub%20Run%2C%20where%20schoolkids%20learn%20about%20plant%20and%20animal%20life.%20The%20company%20has%20received%20a%20special%20zoning%20exemption%20allowing%20it%20to%20build%20a%20110-foot-high%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Graham%2C%20a%20local%20resident%20who%20refers%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbird%20nerd%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20counting%20the%20heron%20nests%20since%20last%20spring.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20a%2010-story%20data%20center%20in%20my%20backyard%2C%20but%2C%20moreover%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20kill%20generations%20of%20birds%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%20Penzance%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWater%20supplies%20are%20also%20at%20risk.%20Many%20of%20the%20planned%20data%20centers%20being%20built%20in%20Prince%20William%20County%20will%20be%20sited%20in%20a%20catchment%20area%20for%20the%20Occoquan%20Reservoir%2C%20which%20provides%20the%20drinking%20water%20for%20800%2C000%20people%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%2C%20including%20many%20residents%20of%20Fairfax%20County%20(and%20which%20once%20spawned%20a%2066-pound%2C%204-ounce%20catfish%20that%20set%20a%20state%20record.).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fairfaxcounty.gov%2Fenvironment-energy-coordination%2Fsites%2Fenvironment-energy-coordination%2Ffiles%2FAssets%2FFINAL%25202024%2520ARE%2520%2520ADA_A-1a.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20report%20for%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Fairfax's%20Environmental%20Quality%20Advisory%20Council%20identified%20elevated%20levels%20of%20salt%2C%20which%20can%20come%20from%20data%20center%20wastewater%2C%20as%20a%20particular%20worry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20warns%20that%20the%20approval%20of%20large%20data%20centers%20using%20evaporative%20cooling%20risked%20%26quot%3Bblowdown%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20reservoir%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bwould%20increase%20salt%20in%20a%20water%20source%20already%20stressed%20by%20salt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20data%20center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f1a3fe8d3928365ba2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Yondr%20data%20center%20near%20the%20Briarfield%20Estates%20neighborhood%20in%20Ashburn.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20data%20center%20companies%20are%20moving%20away%20from%20reliance%20on%20water%20for%20cooling.%20The%20two%20companies%20developing%20Prince%20William%20County's%20big%20Digital%20Gateway%20project%2C%20Compass%20and%20QTS%2C%20both%20said%20their%20facilities%20won't%20use%20water%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20environmental%20agencies%20have%20found%20at%20least%20two%20data%20centers%20out%20of%20compliance%20with%20the%20Clean%20Water%20Act%2C%20including%20a%20QTS%20facility%20in%20Piscataway%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20QTS%20has%20said%20that%20it%20failed%20to%20complete%20required%20sampling%20and%20reporting%20at%20one%20site.%20It%20agreed%20to%20implement%20compliance%20measures%20and%20settled%20the%20violations%20without%20an%20admission%20of%20fault%2C%20paying%20a%20penalty%20of%20%24179%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jessica%20Buhl%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Prince%20William%20and%20enjoys%20watching%20the%20goldfinches%20and%20other%20birds%20outside%20her%20window%20about%20a%20mile%20from%20the%20proposed%20Digital%20Gateway%2C%20said%20she%20worries%20about%20contaminants%20in%20her%20well%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Buhl%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f1e68a292900801323d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Buhl%20is%20worried%20about%20a%20proposed%20data%20center%20development%20a%20mile%20from%20her%20home%20in%20Prince%20William%20County.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuhl%2C%20whose%20license%20plate%20on%20her%20GMC%20Yukon%20Denali%20reads%20%26quot%3BNOPWDG%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20Prince%20William%20Digital%20Gateway%2C%20said%20she%20had%20been%20looking%20at%20houses%20in%20Maine.%20She's%20just%20not%20ready%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20give%20up%20the%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Buntil%20it's%20really%2C%20truly%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20has%20irked%20Buhl%20and%20some%20other%20local%20residents%20is%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20build-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Prince%20William%20County%2C%20the%20board%20of%20supervisors%20moved%20quickly%20to%20rezone%20the%20Digital%20Gateway%20project%20and%20approved%20what%20would%20be%20a%2037-facility%20campus%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Manassas%20National%20Battlefield%20Park.%20When%20the%20project%20is%20completed%2C%20dozens%20of%20data%20center%20buildings%20and%20high-voltage%20transmission%20lines%20will%20permanently%20alter%20the%20park's%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20park%20includes%20a%20Confederate%20cemetery%20and%20other%20spots%20on%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places.%20The%20American%20Battlefield%20Trust%20has%20sued%20to%20stop%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20encompasses%20land%20that%20once%20belonged%20to%20the%20Thornton%20settlement%2C%20a%20community%20of%20free%20Blacks%2C%20and%20the%20plantation%20home%20of%20Jennie%20Dean%2C%20a%20freed%20woman%20who%20established%20a%20school%20and%20congregations%20in%20the%20area%20in%20the%20late%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20Gateway%20south%20is%20almost%20entirely%20covered%20by%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kulick%2C%20the%20HOA%20organizer%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Prince%20William%20County%20Historical%20Commission%2C%20which%20opposed%20the%20rezoning.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20face%20of%20all%20that%2C%20what%20do%20we%20protect%3F%20What's%20important%20enough%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20QTS%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20about%20800%20acres%20of%20the%20project%20were%20set%20to%20be%20protected%2C%20and%20that%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20donate%20land%2C%20install%20interactive%20kiosks%2C%20and%20create%20trails%20in%20local%20parks%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Manassas%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompass%20agreed%20to%20buffers%20of%201%2C500%20feet%20between%20the%20project%20and%20other%20landowners%2C%20Katy%20Hancock%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20by%20email.%20Open%20space%20will%20cover%2039%25%20of%20the%20884%20acres%20Compass%20owns%20as%20part%20of%20the%20development%2C%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20Compass%20agreed%20to%20plant%20650%20trees%20an%20acre%20in%20those%20areas%20if%20older%20trees%20needed%20to%20come%20down%20during%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20effect%20on%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20centers%20require%20backup%20power%2C%20which%20means%20installing%20dozens%20of%20industrial-size%20diesel%20generators%20made%20by%20manufacturers%20like%20Caterpillar.%20An%20Amazon%20facility%20next%20to%20the%20Great%20Oak%20neighborhood%20is%20permitted%20for%2097%20diesel%20generators%20spread%20over%20four%20buildings.%20Multiply%20that%20over%20hundreds%20of%20buildings%20across%20Northern%20Virginia%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20diesel%20generators%20easily%20climbs%20into%20the%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20centers%20have%20contributed%20to%20regional%20air%20pollution%20%E2%80%94%20albeit%20less%20than%204%25%20of%20the%20regional%20emissions%20of%20nitrogen%20oxides%2C%20according%20to%20the%20state%20legislature's%20report.%20State%20officials%20were%20conducting%20further%20study%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20which%20said%20most%20data%20center%20sites%20experienced%20no%20more%20than%20two%20minor%20outages%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20nearly%20all%20lasting%20a%20few%20hours.%20Companies%20also%20test%20generators%20periodically%20to%20ensure%20proper%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%2C%20the%20self-described%20bird%20nerd%2C%20witnessed%20one%20such%20event%20recently%20when%20he%20stopped%20at%20a%20gas%20station%20in%20Sterling%2C%20Virginia%2C%20in%20late%20January.%20The%20generators%20of%20a%20nearby%20data%20center%20were%20running%20so%20loud%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20talk%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20generators'%20exhaust%20caps%20%26quot%3Bwere%20full%20bore%2C%20wide%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20hear%20them%20and%20see%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20coal%20plant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238f1dc6ad288d1480d035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDominion%20Energy%2C%20Virginia's%20largest%20utility%2C%20has%20proposed%20building%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20at%20the%20former%20coal-fired%20Chesterfield%20Power%20Station%20outside%20of%20Richmond.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Sabin%2C%20an%2080-year-old%20former%20cabinet%20maker%20and%20science%20teacher%2C%20lives%20200%20feet%20from%20the%20proposed%20Digital%20Gateway%20project.%20He%20has%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%2C%20brought%20on%20by%20a%20lifetime%20of%20smoking%2C%20and%20requires%20oxygen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Virginia%2C%20many%20facilities%20are%20being%20built%20years%20before%20they%20can%20get%20hooked%20up%20to%20the%20electricity%20grid%2C%20and%20Sabin%20worries%20that%20government%20officials%20will%20let%20them%20run%20on%20diesel%20generators%20until%20they%20can%20connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20really%20has%20me%20concerned%20is%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20ram%20this%20thing%20through%20before%20adequate%20power%20has%20a%20way%20of%20getting%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Digital%20Gateway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Virginia's%20Department%20of%20Environmental%20Quality%20said%20it%20hadn't%20received%20any%20such%20requests%20and%20expected%20data%20centers%20to%20comply%20with%20all%20applicable%20air%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESabin%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20are%20among%20a%20group%20of%20plaintiffs%20who%20have%20sued%20to%20block%20the%20Digital%20Gateway%2C%20have%20discussed%20the%20prospect%20of%20leaving%20their%20home%20of%2040%20years%20if%20their%20legal%20challenge%20isn't%20successful.%20%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20we%20wanted%20to%20die%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOperating%20at%20just%207%25%20of%20their%20permitted%20limits%2C%20data%20center%20generators%20nationwide%20emit%20around%202%2C500%20tons%20of%20nitrous%20oxide%20annually%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%2C%20which%20ran%20air%20center%20permits%20from%20every%20state%20with%20a%20data%20center%20through%20an%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20tool%20that%20calculates%20public%20health%20burden.%20That's%20equivalent%20to%20the%20air%20pollutants%20emitted%20by%20over%202%20million%20passenger%20cars%20making%20a%20round-trip%20drive%20between%20New%20York%20and%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20data%20centers%20operate%20their%20generators%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law.%20Business%20Insider%20found%2056%20civil%20penalties%20across%20nine%20states%20levied%20against%20tech%20companies%20because%20their%20centers%20were%20found%20to%20have%20violated%20air%20quality%20regulations%2C%20with%20fines%20totaling%20at%20least%20%241.4%20million.%20The%20companies%20with%20the%20most%20penalties%20were%20CyrusOne%2C%20with%20seven%2C%20and%20Equinix%2C%20with%20six%2C%20followed%20by%20QTS%20with%20four%20and%20Amazon%20with%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Equinix%20said%20the%20company%20had%20been%20out%20of%20compliance%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20few%20limited%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20aggressively%20work%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20facilities%20are%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20all%20applicable%20regulations.%20A%20CyrusOne%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20committed%20to%20environmental%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said%20it%20had%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20environmental%20compliance.%20QTS%20said%20violations%20at%20its%20data%20centers%20had%20been%20addressed%20and%20the%20company%20was%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20the%20Clean%20Air%20Act%20and%20the%20Clean%20Water%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2025%2F05%2F2025-05-data-centers-healthcost%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22cartogram%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22scrolly%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20may%20become%20a%20bigger%20concern%20as%20state%20officials%20grapple%20with%20the%20precariousness%20of%20Virginia's%20grid.%20During%20a%20particularly%20intense%20heat%20wave%20in%20Virginia%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20thousands%20of%20Dominion%20Energy%20customers%20lost%20power%20over%20a%2010-day%20stretch%2C%20according%20to%20Find%20Energy%2C%20which%20compiled%20outage%20counts%20from%20utilities%2C%20solar%20providers%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20other%20sources.%20A%20Dominion%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20outages%20were%20triggered%20by%20severe%20thunderstorms%20common%20there%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20and%20that%20the%20utility%20was%20significantly%20reducing%20storm-related%20outages%20with%20measures%20such%20as%20burying%20power%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20has%20his%20way%2C%20Kaya%2C%20the%20resident%20of%20Amberleigh%20Station%2C%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20those%20impacts%20for%20much%20longer.%20He%20and%20his%20family%20are%20looking%20to%20move%2C%20ideally%20to%20more%20mountainous%20terrain%20that%20is%20inhospitable%20to%20data%20center%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dream%20was%20to%20buy%20a%20place%2C%20own%20that%20place%2C%20and%20raise%20my%20children%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20that%20pretty%20much%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2025%2F04%2F2025-04-data-centers-header-itsucks%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257cd731f-ba03-42f2-87fd-3dbe218db4f7%5C%22%3ESeries%20Credits%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20data%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%20used%20air%20permits%20issued%20to%20data%20center%20backup%20generators%20to%20identify%20facility%20location%20and%20ownership%2C%20and%20estimate%20facility%20power%20use.%20We%20received%20permits%20from%20all%20but%20four%20states%2C%20plus%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20Business%20Insider%20also%20used%202020%20US%20census%20data%20and%20data%20from%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%E2%80%99s%20COBRA%2C%20AVERT%2C%20and%20EJSCREEN%20tools.%20Read%20more%20about%20how%20we%20investigated%20the%20impact%20of%20data%20center%20growth%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHannah%20Beckler%2C%20Dakin%20Campbell%2C%20Daniel%20Geiger%2C%20Rosemarie%20Ho%2C%20Narimes%20Parakul