%94%20%E2%80%9Clife%20is%20full%20of%20pluses%20and%20minuses%E2%80%9D.%20His%20genius%20lay%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20bring%20an%20emotional%20depth%20to%20every%20conversation.%20Jui%20shares%20an%20anecdote%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20engineering%20days%2C%20I%20did%20not%20score%20well%2C%20this%20one%20time.%20When%20I%20told%20Papa%2C%20he%20showed%20me%20his%20engineering%20report%20card%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20among%20the%20top%20three.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20marks%20were%20not%20important%2C%20but%20one%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkare%E2%80%99s%20precision%20was%20razor-sharp%20on%20the%20field%20and%20off%20it%2C%20too.%20%E2%80%9CPapa%20maintained%20well-manicured%20lawns%2C%20he%20had%20an%20eye%20for%20detail%2C%20and%20loved%20gardening.%20He%20encouraged%20my%20siblings%20and%20me%20to%20plant%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jui%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20he%20started%20dabbling%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F122140%2Fwooden-toys-sawantwadi-rural-art-maharashtra-crafts-tradition%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreating%20wood%20artefacts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accumulating%20driftwood%2C%20and%20chiselling%20them%20into%20beautiful%20art.%20The%20injuries%20he%20would%20sustain%20while%20working%20with%20the%20wood%2C%20or%20even%20during%20encounters%2C%20did%20not%20fluster%20him.%20They%20were%20his%20badges%20of%20bravery.%20But%20these%20moments%20that%20the%20family%20had%20with%20him%20were%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20Karkare%E2%80%99s%20first%20duty%20was%20to%20the%20people%20he%20served.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJui%20would%20often%20ask%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20you%20get%20exhausted%20helping%20people%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%E2%80%99d%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20became%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20because%20no%20other%20profession%20gives%20you%