Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flockheed-martin-shares-fall-pentagon-f35-requests-air-force-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20starting%20my%20own%20business.%20That%20was%20when%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20theoretical%20underpinnings%20of%20business.%20Getting%20an%20MBA%20felt%20like%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20applying%20to%20several%20business%20schools%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-insead-business-school-mba-program-consulting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EINSEAD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwharton-business-school-upenn-ai-curriculum-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWharton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-salaries-stanford-mba-graduates-industries-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStanford%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcambridge-university-library-crowned-britains-best-new-building-riba-stirling-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECambridge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20received%20offers%20from%20INSEAD%20and%20NUS%2C%20and%20picked%20NUS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae4b1261-53ae-426f-a6bc-e743c06420c4%5C%22%3EInternational%20schools%20offer%20something%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20MBA.%20When%20people%20think%20about%20getting%20an%20MBA%2C%20they%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20you%20go%20to%20a%20US%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20wasn't%20what%20I%20wanted%20from%20my%20MBA%20journey%2C%20so%20I%20considered%20international%20schools.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20people%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20to%20challenge%20myself%20intellectually%20and%20culturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20you%20can%20get%20diversity%20from%20atten