0couldn't%20do%20if%20I%20were%20studying%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurriculum-wise%2C%20I've%20had%20some%20really%20all-star%20professors.%20I%20am%20also%20active%20in%20extracurricular%20activities.%20I%20am%20the%20president%20of%20the%20business%20school's%20cultural%2C%20social%2C%20and%20community%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20a%20case%20competition%20with%20my%20classmates%2C%20too.%20We%20flew%20to%20Paris%20to%20compete%2C%20and%20we%20managed%20to%20win%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20gripe%20is%20that%20it's%20been%20too%20fast.%20The%20program%20is%20only%20for%2018%20months%2C%20so%20the%20MBA%20will%20be%20over%20in%20a%20snap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22462f24fe-ac43-447f-804e-487fe9438469%5C%22%3ETrump's%20crackdown%20on%20student%20visas%20could%20be%20a%20silver%20lining%20for%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20friends%20right%20now%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20visas%20so%20they%20can%20do%20a%20short-term%20exchange%20in%20the%20US.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20set%20up%20meetings%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20messed%20up%20right%20now.%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-universities-trying-poach-harvard-students-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrackdown%20on%20student%20visas%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20just%20hurt%20the%20students%20who%20want%20to%20study%20in%20the%20US.%20It%20also%20hurts%20domestic%20students%20who%20are%20now%20less%20likely%20to%20interact%20with%20students%20from%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20think%20there's%20a%20silver%20lining%20to%20all%20this%20chaos.%20For%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20the%20Ivy%20League%20universities%20are%20seen%20as%20the%20bastions%20of%20knowledge%2C%20and%20to%20a%20degree%2C%20they%20are.%20But%20this%20means%20some%20people%20might%20be%20overlooking%20the%20value%20that%20other%20institutions%20have%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20may%20start%20looking%20at%20other%20options%20given%20the%20situation%2C%20and%20that%20can%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20studying%20in%20Singapore.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20more%20outside%20the%20classroom%20than%20inside%20it%2C%20and%20that's%20saying%20something%20because%20we%20study%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20education%20is%20not%20defined%20by%20what%20classroom%20you're%20sitting%20in.%20It's%20about%20what%20you%20learn%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20you%20apply%20your%20knowledge%20in%20your%20life%20after%20graduation.%20Many%20institutions%20can%20prime%20you%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-doing-mba-asia-us-visa-chaos-silver-lining-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750118881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684bc6753d5881a51c1b5953%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-doing-mba-asia-us-visa-chaos-silver-lining-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ryan%20Wall%20earned%20an%20engineering%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder%20and%20is%20now%20pursuing%20an%20MBA%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-doing-mba-asia-us-visa-chaos-silver-lining-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Organization%20enters%20mobile%20phone%20business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750117937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F131a%2Flive%2F8e324230-4ae5-11f0-acc2-694ff49b214c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.