e%20apparently%20accidental%20oversharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20warning%20message%2C%20which%20was%20visible%20Monday%2C%20shows%20up%20after%20you%20hit%20%26quot%3Bshare%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20chat%20in%20the%20Meta%20AI%20app.%20The%20message%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BPrompts%20you%20post%20are%20public%20and%20visible%20to%20everyone.%20Your%20prompts%20may%20be%20suggested%20by%20Meta%20on%20other%20Meta%20apps.%20Avoid%20sharing%20personal%20or%20sensitive%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20warning%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BPost%20to%20feed%26quot%3B%20button%20is%20disabled%20until%20you%20tap%20once%20more%20on%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20screen.%20Only%20%3Cem%3Ethen%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20you%20post%20to%20the%20public%20Discover%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc4ef9df-0c6f-47c1-b3bb-fffb792ff3c4%5C%22%3EMeta%20AI's%20feed%20had%20eerily%20personal%20information%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20asking%20about%20a%20check%20to%20meta%20AI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68483fdcf748d8c055f35f99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20old%20Meta%20AI%20feed%20was%20littered%20with%20personal%20messages%20like%20this%20one.%3Cp%3EMeta%20AI%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%20%2F%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20AI%2C%20the%20stand-alone%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20has%20its%20%26quot%3BDiscover%26quot%3B%20feed%20for%20people%20to%20share%20images%20they%20created%20with%20AI%20or%20to%20post%20their%20chats%20with%20the%20bot.%20These%20chats%20aren't%20public%20by%20default%3B%20you've%20always%20had%20to%20click%20%26quot%3Bshare%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Bpost%26quot%3B%20to%20send%20your%20chats%20to%20the%20Discover%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20it%20seems%20some%20users%20didn't%20understand%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20under%20the%20previous%20system.%20(One%20man%20I%20talked%20to%20last%20week%20said%20he%20hadn't%20meant%20to%20post%20his%20conversation%20with%20the%20chatbot%20on%20car%20repair.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20app%20first%20launched%20in%20late%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-app-public-feed-warning-how-2025-05%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20wrote%20about%20the%20problem%20of%20accidental%20public%20posts%20on%20Meta%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Checking%20back%20last%20week%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20problem%20seemed%20even%20worse%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20now%20way%20more%20posts%20that%20seemed%20to%20be%20clearly%20shared%20by%20mistake.%20Some%20of%20these%20included%20intimate%20personal%20issues%2C%20like%20asking%20for%20help%20drafting%20a%20letter%20to%20a%20judge%20about%20child%20custody%2C%20medical%20issues%2C%20and%20relationship%20quandaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fventuretwins%2Fstatus%2F1932934055378759805%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20found%20examples%20of%20people%20posting%20tax%20information%2C%20or%20seeming%20not%20to%20even%20understand%20what%20they%20were%20using%2C%20like%20a%20person%20who%20asked%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20they%20put%20a%20deep%20heat%20cream%20on%20their%20private%20parts%2C%20but%20then%20asked%20the%20bot%20to%20keep%20the%20conversation%20private%20(on%20a%20public%20feed).%20Hmm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205ce0063-273a-4679-8797-e97945418688%5C%22%3EMeta%20AI's%20new%20pop-up%20warns%20people%20before%20posting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20AI%20gives%20a%20business%20news%20update%20with%20a%20warning%20about%20posting%20publically%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68506b95f748d8c055f3c8d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20a%20new%20warning%20message%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20scr