jo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20new%20gas%20station%20plans%20and%20said%20the%20station%20is%20expected%20to%20open%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDocuments%20filed%20with%20the%20city%20planning%20office%20say%20the%20project%20will%20involve%20the%20demolition%20of%20a%20former%20Bed%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond%20store%20and%20suggest%20the%20new%20fuel%20center%20will%20be%20doing%20brisk%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20nine%20fuel%20truck%20deliveries%20are%20expected%20each%20day%2C%20with%20more%20than%209%2C500%20vehicles%20stopping%20to%20fill%20their%20tanks%20between%205%20a.m.%20and%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%20The%20company%20doesn't%20typically%20discuss%20new%20locations%20more%20than%20three%20months%20before%20their%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGas%20is%20big%20business%20for%20Costco%2C%20which%20touts%20cost%20savings%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-early-shopping-hours-executive-membership-perk-return-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop%20perks%20of%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Gasoline%20sales%20represented%20nearly%20one%20in%20eight%20dollars%20the%20company%20made%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%2430%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Costco's%20annual%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20executives%20have%20said%20in%20numerous%20earnings%20calls%20that%20they%20aim%20to%20keep%20their%20prices%20below%20the%20competition%20in%20a%20given%20area%2C%20and%20that's%20before%20the%205%25%20rewards%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcostco-anywhere-visa-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECostco%20credit%20cardholders%3C%2Fa%3E%20get%20on%20fuel%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20gas%20off-site%20could%20help%20Costco%20alleviate%20some%20of%20the%20traffic%20that%20is%20bedeviling%20some%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-ceo-packed-parking-lots-sign-new-location-coming-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusier%20warehouses'%20parking%20lots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20members%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20fight%20the%20crowds%20for%20a%20fuel-only%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Ron%20Vachris%20has%20said%20several%20times%20that%20the%20company%20is%20looking%20at%20different%20ways%20it%20can%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%26quot%3B%20cannibalize%20the%20business%20of%20nearby%20warehouses%20that%20are%20straining%20under%20too%20much%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeldman%20thinks%20the%20strategy%20is%20likely%20focused%20on%20areas%20where%20Costco%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bdensity%20of%20membership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20competitive%20market%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20an%20effort%20to%20continue%20to%20provide%20more%20benefits%20to%20their%20members%2C%20and%20to%20try%20to%20retain%20them%20and%20keep%20them%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-to-build-new-stand-alone-gas-station-in-california-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750103386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68505cfd85e81483682c2e81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-to-build-new-stand-alone-gas-station-in-california-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Costco%20is%20planning%20to%20build%20a%2040-bay%20gas%20station%20on%20the%20site%20of%20a%20former%20Bed%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond%20store%2C%20two%20miles%20from%20its%20nearest%20warehouse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-to-build-new-stand-alone-gas-station-in-california-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20needed%20a%20durable%20sofa%20bed%20that%20could%20keep%20up%20with%20my%20family%20of%206%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20this%20one%20from%20Cozey%20is%20modular%2C%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20has%20storage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20cozey%20neptune%20sectional%20in%20an%20L-shape%20in%20a%20living%20room%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848a7383d5881a51c1b285e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20uniquely%20modular%20Cozey%20Neptune%20Sofa%20Bed%20has%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20movie%20nights%20to%20sleepovers%20for%20my%20family%20of%20six.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20room%20is%20awkwardly%20shaped%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20find%20a%20sofa%20that%20fit%20the%20long%2C%20narrow%20room%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20sofa%20that%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20sleeper%20for%20our%20frequent%20guests.%20Most%20sofas%20were%20too%20small%20for%20my%20family%20of%20six%2C%20or%20so%20big%20they%20overwhelmed%20the%20room.%20Making%20the%20challenge%20of%20finding%20a%20sofa%20even%20more%20difficult%20is%20that%20I%20wanted%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%20that%20is%20comfortable.%20Plus%2C%20I%20preferred%20a%20sofa%20with%20a%20performance%20fabric%20that%20is%20durable%20and%20stain-resistant.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D625efdee459bd32d3481ff8a542d2a6efebd48d8de6693b788d1e3bc70894d8d%26postID%3D6848969814270c4174ad1f38%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcozey-neptune-sofa-bed-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcozeypartnershipsusa.sjv.io%252Fc%252F196318%252F1699716%252F19752%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.cozey.com%25252Fproduct%25252Fseating%25252Fneptune%25252Fneptune-fog-full-bed-3-seater-arms-regular%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECozey%20Neptune%20Sofa%20Bed%3C%2Fa%3E%20checked%20all%20the%20boxes.%20Bonus%2C%20it's%20modular%20to%20be%20as%20small%20or%20large%20as%20I%20desire%20and%20has%20built-in%20storage%20in%20the%20cushions%2C%20a%20unique%20feature%20that%20lets%20me%20store%20blankets%20and%20guests'%20bedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECozey%20sells%20directly%20to%20consumers%20and%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa-couch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20a%20couch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20sofas%20are%20sold%20at%20a%20reasonable%20price%20point%2C%20given%20the%20quality%20and%20level%20of%20customization%20available.%20After%20using%20the%20Neptune%20for%20about%20six%20weeks%2C%20I'm%20very%20pleased%20with%20how%20it%20looks%20and%20how%20well%20its%20premium%20plywood%20frame%2C%20high-density%20foam%20cushions%2C%20and%20stain-resistant%20premium%20fabric%20stands%20up%20to%20my%20busy%20(and%20messy)%20family%20of%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d36d4681-9f2b-4621-856e-48a2dd9831e9%5C%22%3EDesign%20and%20Customizations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gif%20of%20cozey%20sofa%20assembly%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848acb185e81483682bd6be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECozey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECozey%20specializes%20in%20modular%20sofas.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20the%20Neptune%20offers%20several%20seating%20options%2C%20with%20and%20without%20ottomans%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20sleepers.%20The%20modularity%20of%20the%20design%20lets%20you%20select%20a%20single%20or%20full-size%20sleeper%20sofa%20comprised%20of%20one%20to%20four%20seats%20starting%20at%20%241%2C890%20or%20a%20massive%209-seater%20U-shaped%20sectional%20design%20with%20a%20full-size%20bed%20that%20costs%20just%20over%20%245%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20select%20your%20base%20combination%2C%20you%20can%20add%20headrests%20and%20ottomans%2C%20storage%20seats%2C%20a%20sleeper%20option%2C%20and%20your%20preferred%20color.%20The%20storage%20ottomans%20can%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20couch%2C%20used%20freestanding%20as%20extra%20seating%20or%20footrests%2C%20or%20attached%20to%20the%20sleeper%20to%20create%20a%20larger%20sleeping%20surface.%20They%20can%20also%20hold%20up%20to%2032%20liters%2C%20like%20pillows%20or%20extra%20bedding.%20I%20also%20use%20one%20of%20the%20ottomans%20to%20store%20wayward%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20wanted%20the%20biggest%20sofa%20possible%20without%20crowding%20my%20narrow%20family%20room%2C%20I%20appreciated%20that%20Cozey's%20online%20design%20tool%20showed%20me%20the%20dimensions%20of%20each%20configuration%20I%20created.%20After%20a%20little%20trial-and-error%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20sofa%20that%20was%20just%20right%20for%20my%20space%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Neptune%20is%20available%20in%20five%20different%20colors%20and%20two%20different%20fabrics.%20The%20Neptune's%20standard%20durable%20child%20pet-friendly%20performance%20fabric%20comes%20in%20Slate%20(dark%20gray)%2C%20Fog%20(light%20gray)%2C%20Latte%20(beige)%2C%20and%20Leaf%20(green).%20It%20also%20comes%20in%20a%20water-%20and%20stain-resistant%20Aquaforte%20fabric%20in%20Snowdrift%20(white).%20Cozey%20sends%20free%20fabric%20swatches%20upon%20request%20if%20you%20want%20to%20get%20a%20close-up%20of%20their%20color%20options%20before%20ordering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciate%20that%20Cozey%20has%20a%20generous%2030-day%20return%20policy%2C%20where%20you%20can%20ship%20the%20sofa%20back%20for%20free%2C%20but%20you%20will%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20original%20boxes.%20With%20Cozey%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20easily%20return%20excess%20seats%20and%20receive%20a%20full%20refund%20if%20I%20decided%20a%20sofa%20with%20a%20smaller%20footprint%20was%20better.%20Alternatively%2C%20if%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20squeeze%20in%20an%20extra%20seat%20or%20two%2C%20thanks%20to%20Cozey's%20modular%20design%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20order%20additional%20seats%20easily.%20Cozey%20also%20offers%20a%20five-year%20warranty%20that%20covers%20defective%20parts%2C%20where%20they%20will%20replace%20the%20affected%20section%2C%20but%20not%20the%20entire%20sofa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8fbca80-1b72-4011-9265-d5ba56e50172%5C%22%3EOrdering%20and%20Delivery%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22several%20boxes%20from%20cozey%20of%20the%20sofa%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848a710f748d8c055f36fe9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20order%20shipped%20in%2016%20different%20boxes%3B%20each%20seat%20shipped%20individually%20and%20was%20clearly%20labeled%2C%20but%20you'll%20need%20to%20find%20some%20floor%20space%20to%20fit%20all%20the%20boxes%20before%20assembly.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Smith%20Davis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECozey's%20ordering%20page%20lets%20you%20easily%20see%20your%20desired%20configuration%20in%20both%20sit%20and%20sleep%20orientations.%20They%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20dimensions%20and%20have%20an%20AR%20feature%20to%20let%20you%20see%20what%20the%20sofa%20could%20look%20like%20in%20your%20space.%20If%20you%20aren't%20sure%20what%20you%20need%2C%20Cozey%20offers%20a%20free%20design%20consultation%20via%20video%20or%20telephone.%20Once%20you%20settle%20on%20the%20configuration%2C%20color%2C%20and%20accessories%20you%20want%2C%20add%20your%20design%20to%20your%20cart%20and%20place%20your%20order.%20Cozey%20lists%20each%20individual%20piece%20in%20your%20cart%20so%20you%20can%20double-check%20exactly%20which%20pieces%20you%20are%20getting%20before%20you%20hit%20%26quot%3Bbuy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelivery%20was%20fast%20and%20free%20via%20FedEx.%20Cozey%20ships%20in%20the%20United%20States%20except%20Alaska%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20the%20Virgin%20Islands%2C%20and%20is%20also%20available%20throughout%20Canada.%20I%20received%20my%20Neptune%2013%20days%20after%20placing%20my%20order.%20It%20arrived%20in%2016%20different%20boxes%2C%20clearly%20labeled%20with%20a%20number%20and%20which%20piece%20was%20inside.%20Although%20my%20sofa%20came%20in%20a%20surprisingly%20large%20number%20of%20boxes%2C%20the%20system%20worked%20well.%20Each%20box%20weighed%20under%2055%20pounds%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20move%20the%20boxes%20inside%20myself%20and%20easily%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20pieces%20as%20I%20assembled%20the%20sofa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220dbe2470-c761-4a8c-b57b-cff0c32164cf%5C%22%3ESet-Up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20kids%20work%20to%20assemble%20the%20cozey%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848a95885e81483682bd69f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECozey's%20website%20makes%20setting%20up%20the%20sofa%20look%20simple%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20process%20time-consuming%20and%20challenging.%20I%20followed%20the%20included%20instructions%2C%20but%20I%20struggled%20at%20times%20to%20line%20up%20the%20many%20interlocking%20pieces%20that%20hold%20the%20sofa%20together.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20attempted%20to%20assemble%20the%20sofa%20together%20on%20my%20own.%20However%2C%20I%20became%20frustrated%20when%20I%20couldn't%20get%20several%20pieces%20to%20lock%20together.%20Once%20my%20teenage%20daughter%20and%20young%20son%20pitched%20in%20to%20help%2C%20things%20went%20much%20more%20smoothly.%20It%20was%20helpful%20to%20have%20someone%20guide%20me%20in%20placing%20the%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECozey%20estimates%20that%20assembling%20one%20of%20its%20sofas%20takes%20between%20five%20and%2010%20minutes%20per%20seat.%20However%2C%20it%20took%20me%20twice%20as%20long%20to%20assemble%20my%20six-seater%20sofa%2C%20including%20attaching%20legs%20to%20the%20seats%2C%20placing%20the%20cushions%2C%20and%20trying%20two%20different%20configurations.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20process%20probably%20would%20have%20been%20faster%20if%20I%20had%20enlisted%20help%20from%20the%20beginning%20and%20had%20not%20toyed%20with%20different%20configurations.%20Even%20though%20the%20assembly%20process%20was%20more%20of%20a%20hassle%20than%20I%20anticipated%2C%20it%20was%20well%20worth%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228511845-58c8-4594-a7b9-281b9adccb1e%5C%22%3EComfort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Neptune%20has%20firm%20cushions%20made%20out%20of%20high-density%20foam%20that%20softened%20a%20little%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20use.%20My%20entire%20family%20finds%20the%20Neptune%20very%20comfortable.%20My%20son%2C%20who%20prefers%20to%20nap%20in%20his%20bed%2C%20fell%20asleep%20on%20the%20Neptune%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20in%20the%20first%20month%20we%20had%20the%20sofa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22storage%20section%20of%20cozy%20sofa%20with%20a%20blanket%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848a710f748d8c055f36fe8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESimply%20lift%20off%20the%20cushion%20to%20access%20the%20amply-sized%20storage%20compartment%20that%20can%20fit%20extra%20bedding.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20how%20easily%20the%20Neptune%20opens%20and%20closes%20when%20I%20want%20to%20access%20its%20under-seat%20storage%20or%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20sofa%20bed.%20Accessing%20the%20storage%20space%20is%20as%20easy%20as%20lifting%20the%20seat%20and%20removing%20the%20top%20cushion%2C%20which%20I%20often%20do%20to%20retrieve%20the%20blankets%20I%20store%20there.%20For%20the%20storage%20seats%2C%20the%20top%20cushion%20isn't%20attached%20to%20the%20base%2C%20but%20simply%20sits%20on%20top.%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20the%20cushions%20might%20move%20with%20use.%20However%2C%20the%20seats%20don't%20move%20a%20bit%2C%20even%20when%20my%20kids%20are%20being%20wild.%20To%20open%20the%20sleeper%2C%20I%20just%20need%20to%20lift%20the%20bottom%20seat%20of%20the%20convertible%20seats%20and%20pull%20them%20out.%20The%20sleeper%20cushions%20are%20attached%20to%20the%20base%2C%20and%20the%20process%20of%20opening%20them%20is%20very%20smooth.%20It's%20also%20easy%20to%20remove%20the%20back%20cushions%20to%20finish%20creating%20the%20sleeper.%20The%20back%20cushions%20have%20a%20large%20handle%20that%20is%20used%20to%20gently%20lift%20the%20cushions%20before%20laying%20them%20in%20place.%20The%20optional%20ottomans%20can%20be%20used%20to%20extend%20the%20sleeping%20area%20by%20placing%20them%20next%20to%20the%20sleeper%20and%20locking%20them%20into%20place%20with%20a%20small%20metal%20arm%20that%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20extend%20for%20use%20and%20then%20flip%20back%20into%20the%20ottoman%20for%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8d2d45c-69d6-4280-b6dd-b3f98f7ede82%5C%22%3ESleeping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20neptune%20sofa%20converted%20to%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6848a721f748d8c055f36fef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20very%20intuitive%20to%20convert%20the%20Neptune%20sleeper%20into%20a%20bed%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20a%20traditional%20sleeper%20and%20does%20not%20come%20with%20a%20mattress.%20Instead%2C%20the%20sofa%20transforms%20into%20a%20bed%20by%20pulling%20out%20specially%20designed%20seats%20to%20expand%20them%20into%20a%20sleeping%20surface%20and%20then%20placing%20the%20back%20cushions%20in%20the%20space%20created%20by%20pulling%20out%20the%20seat.%20Notably%2C%20because%20of%20Neptune's%20modular%20design%2C%20there%20is%20flexibility%20on%20how%20you%20set%20up%20the%20sleeper.%20I%20ordered%20two%20sleeper%20seats%20and%20placed%20them%20next%20to%20each%20other%20to%20create%20one%20large%20sleeping%20space.%20However%2C%20because%20the%20sleeper%20seats%20are%20separate%2C%20I%20could%20move%20one%20of%20the%20seats%20to%20a%20different%20position%20at%20any%20time%20to%20create%20two%20single%20beds.%20This%20might%20come%20in%20handy%20when%20my%20niece%20and%20nephew%20come%20to%20visit%2C%20if%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20sleep%20next%20to%20each%20other.%20However%2C%20since%20one%20of%20my%20sleeper%20seats%20is%20a%20corner%20seat%2C%20that%20seat%20needs%20to%20stay%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20initially%20ordered%20the%20sleeper%20sofa%20for%20overnight%20guests%2C%20my%20kids%20regularly%20expand%20the%20sofa%20to%20use%20as%20a%20lounger%20for%20family%20movie%20nights%20and%20hang-outs%20with%20friends.%20I%20was%20surprised%20and%20happy%20to%20find%20that%20my%20kids%20find%20the%20sofa%20bed%20easy%20enough%20to%20set%20up%20themselves%20and%20comfortable%20enough%20that%20they%20want%20to%20use%20it%20regularly.%20Given%20the%20higher%20cost%20of%20sleeper%20sofas%2C%20it's%20nice%20to%20see%20that%20this%20feature%20is%20getting%20more%20than%20occasional%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20sure%20Neptune's%20sofa%20bed%20would%20be%20comfortable%20for%20my%20guests%2C%20I%20slept%20on%20it%20for%20a%20few%20nights%20myself.%20While%20it's%20not%20as%20comfortable%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ftempur-pedic-proadapt-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETempur-Pedic%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20usually%20sleep%20on%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20comfortable%20than%20the%20thin%2C%20lumpy%20mattresses%20I%20associate%20with%20most%20sofa%20beds.%20Since%20the%20bed%20portion%20consists%20of%20the%20sofa's%20firm%20cushions%2C%20the%20sleep%20surface%20is%20firm.%20While%20sleeping%20on%20the%20sofa%20bed%2C%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20I%20would%20feel%20the%20spacing%20between%20the%20cushions.%20While%20I%20could%20feel%20them%2C%20they%20weren't%20very%20noticeable%20once%20I%20lay%20down%20to%20go%20to%20sleep.%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20sofa%20with%20my%20partner%20one%20night.%20Because%20each%20section%20of%20the%20sleeper%20is%20separate%2C%20his%20movements%20didn't%20bother%20me%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20wake%20up%20when%20he%20got%20out%20of%20bed%20earlier%20than%20me.%20As%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20I%20was%20also%20concerned%20that%20the%20thick%2C%20durable%20fabric%20might%20trap%20heat%2C%20but%20I%20was%20relieved%20to%20find%20that%20I%20didn't%20overheat%20at%20night.%20Although%20Neptune's%20sleeper%20isn't%20as%20comfortable%20as%20a%20regular%20mattress%2C%20I%20found%20it%20far%20more%20comfortable%20than%20a%20hotel%20sleeper%20sofa%20I%20recently%20slept%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20solution%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20ensure%20their%20guests%20have%20a%20smooth%20surface.%20Cozey%20offers%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4ce188149bd5fe064a84d0264c4630042fd99f91cd3741391e8fa8a93553a83d%26postID%3D6848969814270c4174ad1f38%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcozey-neptune-sofa-bed-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.cozey.com%252Fproduct%252Fmodules%252Fneptune-sleepkit%252Fneptune-sleep-kit%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeptune%20Sleep%20Kit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20plush%20mattress%20topper%2C%20two%20small%20pillows%2C%20a%20comforter%2C%20and%20sheets%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20fit%20the%20Neptune%20perfectly.%20The%20mattress%20topper%20made%20the%20sleeper%20more%20comfortable%20by%20smoothing%20out%20the%20spaces%20between%20the%20cushions%20that%20make%20up%20the%20sleeping%20surface%20and%20adding%20another%20layer.%20Although%20it's%20nice%20to%20have%20sheets%2C%20a%20comforter%2C%20and%20pillows%20that%20are%20custom-designed%20to%20fit%20the%20sleeper%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20these%20add%20much%20value%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20already%20have%20your%20own%20bedding.%20A%20Cozey%20rep%20said%20that%20only%20about%2020%25%20of%20customers%20add%20on%20the%20Sleep%20Kit.%20If%20Cozey%20sold%20the%20mattress%20topper%20on%20its%20own%2C%20I%20think%20it%20would%20be%20a%20no-brainer%20to%20purchase%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20justify%20the%20%24360%20cost%20for%20the%20entire%20set%20unless%20you%20are%20short%20these%20other%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c15bacb0-d9ae-47c9-9459-040665b894f2%5C%22%3EDurability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20received%20the%20Neptune%20about%20six%20weeks%20ago%2C%20it%20has%20gotten%20heavy%20use.%20My%20family%20uses%20it%20daily%20to%20watch%20television%2C%20and%20we've%20had%20a%20few%20family%20movie%20nights%20where%20we%20all%20watch%20together.%20The%20sofa%20has%20also%20been%20used%20during%20countless%20playdates%20and%20guests%20have%20commented%20how%20much%20they%20like%20the%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20sofa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20my%20kids%20like%20to%20snack%2C%20and%20I%20have%20allowed%20them%20to%20eat%20and%20drink%20on%20the%20sofa%20to%20their%20heart's%20content%20to%20test%20its%20durability%20and%20performance%20fabric.%20The%20sofa%20has%20held%20up%20exceptionally%20well.%20I've%20needed%20to%20vacuum%20the%20sofa%20to%20remove%20crumbs%20several%20times.%20Once%2C%20I%20found%20chocolate%20sauce%20that%20had%20dripped%20down%20the%20front%20of%20a%20cushion%2C%20down%20to%20the%20sofa's%20body%2C%20and%20onto%20the%20floor.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20found%20the%20stain%2C%20it%20had%20been%20sitting%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20my%20new%20sofa%20would%20be%20ruined%20forever.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20the%20chocolate%20syrup%20came%20out%20after%20dabbing%20it%20with%20some%20water.%20Another%20time%2C%20I%20found%20a%20red%20spot%20that%20was%20either%20from%20a%20strawberry%20or%20a%20piece%20of%20candy.%20That%20spot%20came%20out%20equally%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20pleased%20with%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20clean%20the%20Neptune%20that%20I%20regretted%20choosing%20a%20darker%20color%20for%20the%20sofa.%20I%20chose%20Fog%20rather%20than%20the%20lighter%20Latte%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20would%20match%20my%20decor%20better%20but%20couldstain%20too%20easily.%20Now%20that%20I've%20successfully%20removed%20several%20stains%20from%20the%20sofa%2C%20I%20would%20feel%20more%20confident%20ordering%20a%20lighter%20color%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20since%20the%20Neptune%20is%20the%20first%20piece%20of%20modular%20furniture%20I%20have%20owned%2C%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20the%20individual%20pieces%20might%20move%20with%20use%2C%20making%20the%20sofa%20feel%20flimsy.%20After%20heavy%20use%2C%20the%20pieces%20haven't%20moved%20a%20bit.%20I%20briefly%20allowed%20my%20children%20to%20climb%20and%20jump%20on%20the%20sofa%20to%20see%20if%20the%20pieces%20moved%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20pieces%20separating.%20I%20love%20that%20the%20Neptune%20feels%20like%20one%2C%20solid%20piece%20with%20use%2C%20but%20still%20has%20all%20of%20the%20flexibility%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20modular%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243483819